OL,5, A firefighter took a selfie immediately
OL,6, after the Grenfell Tower fire and used 
OL,7, it on his Tinder online dating profile,
OL,8, a London Assembly meeting has heard.   
OL,10,FThe revelation was made during         
OL,11,FWednesday's hearing, in which findings 
OL,12,Fof a damning review into the fire      
OL,13,Fservice's culture were discussed.      
OL,15,FThe review's author Nasir Afzal told   
OL,16,Fthe meeting: "Why did he feel entitled 
OL,17,Fto do that?"                           
OL,19,FThe fire service said it apologised    
OL,20,F"sincerely for his behaviour".         
